# NebulaForge

NebulaForge is a lightweight and extensible workflow automation engine that enables developers to connect services, automate repetitive tasks, and streamline data flows.

## Features

- Modular architecture
- Real-time task monitoring
- Secure API integrations
- Custom workflow creation
- Cross-platform support

